### Hadith 1:305

*Narrated 'Aisha:*

Whenever anyone of us got her menses, she, on becoming clean, used to
take hold of the blood spot and rub the blood off her garment, and pour
water over it and wash that portion thoroughly and sprinkle water over
the rest of the garment. After that she would pray in (with) it.

